  </div>
</section>

<!-- STEPS -->
<div class="steps-section">
  <div class="steps-label">How it works</div>
  <div class="steps-headline">From upload to <em>verdict</em></div>
  <p class="steps-sub">No forms to fill. No waiting days. No jargon.</p>

  <div class="steps-list">

    <!-- STEP 1 -->
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-header">
        <div class="step-badge">1</div>
        <div class="step-meta">
          <div class="step-num-label">Step one</div>
          <div class="step-title">Drop in your legal pack</div>
          <div class="step-time">Takes 10 seconds</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="step-body-text">Download the legal pack ZIP from the auctioneer's website — it's usually a single file containing everything. Drop it straight in. LegalPack AI handles ZIPs, individual PDFs, multiple files, and packs up to 50MB+ with no issues.</p>
      <div class="upload-mockup">
        <div class="upload-icon">📁</div>
        <div class="upload-title">Drop your legal pack here</div>
        <div class="upload-hint">or click to browse · ZIPs split automatically · Address extracted automatically</div>
        <div class="upload-types">
          <span class="upload-type">PDF</span>
          <span class="upload-type">JPG</span>
          <span class="upload-type">PNG</span>
          <span class="upload-type active">ZIP</span>
          <span class="upload-type">Multi-file</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="step-connector">↓</div>

    <!-- STEP 2 -->
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-header">
        <div class="step-badge">2</div>
        <div class="step-meta">
          <div class="step-num-label">Step two · Optional</div>
          <div class="step-title">Paste the auction listing URL</div>
          <div class="step-time">Takes 5 seconds — saves you typing</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="step-body-text">Paste the URL of the lot from the auctioneer's website — Savills, SDL, BidX1, iamsold, Auction House, whoever. We pull the auction house name, lot date, guide price, and property details straight from the page and drop them into your report automatically.</p>
      <div class="url-mockup">
        <div class="url-mockup-label">Auctioneer listing URL</div>
        <div class="url-input-row">
          <div class="url-input-fake">
            🔗 <span>https://www.sdlauctions.co.uk/property-auctions/lot/58-...</span>
          </div>
          <span class="url-tag">Optional</span>
        </div>
        <div class="url-hint-row">✨ Auto-fills into your report:</div>
        <div class="url-autofill-chips">
          <span class="autofill-chip">Auction house</span>
          <span class="autofill-chip">Lot date</span>
          <span class="autofill-chip">Guide price</span>
          <span class="autofill-chip">Property address</span>
          <span class="autofill-chip">Lot number</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="step-connector">↓</div>

    <!-- STEP 3 -->
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-header">
        <div class="step-badge">3</div>
        <div class="step-meta">
          <div class="step-num-label">Step three</div>
          <div class="step-title">Wait 3–4 minutes</div>
          <div class="step-time">Go make a brew</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="step-body-text">The AI reads every single page — title register, special conditions, searches, lease, property information forms, missing document checks — exactly the way a cautious property solicitor would. You'll see a live progress bar while it works.</p>
      <div class="progress-mockup">
        <div class="progress-topbar">
          <div class="progress-title">Analysing legal pack…</div>
          <div class="progress-timer">2m 14s</div>
        </div>
        <div class="progress-stages">
          <div class="progress-stage"><div class="progress-dot done">✓</div><div class="progress-stage-label done">Extracting documents from ZIP</div></div>
          <div class="progress-stage"><div class="progress-dot done">✓</div><div class="progress-stage-label done">Reading title register &amp; plan</div></div>
          <div class="progress-stage"><div class="progress-dot active">●</div><div class="progress-stage-label active">Analysing special conditions of sale…</div></div>
          <div class="progress-stage"><div class="progress-dot waiting"></div><div class="progress-stage-label">Reading searches &amp; lease</div></div>
          <div class="progress-stage"><div class="progress-dot waiting"></div><div class="progress-stage-label">Generating risk report</div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="progress-bar-wrap"><div class="progress-bar-fill"></div></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="step-connector">↓</div>

    <!-- STEP 4 -->
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-header">
        <div class="step-badge">✓</div>
        <div class="step-meta">
          <div class="step-num-label">Done</div>
          <div class="step-title">Your risk report is ready</div>
          <div class="step-time">Saved to your dashboard forever</div>
        </div>
      </div>
